        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: '???', 3: 'When the CPF did its job, we worked hard transporting rations and weapons out of the warehouse. Whenever it shut down, we\\'d have to face swarms of the Corrupted.'}"
